Here you can enjoy fresh baked cheese cakes, European pastries, panini sandwiches and many other desserts and baked fancies.
We are proud to carry and sell our own exclusive line of gourmet coffee beans brewed by the cup or to take home by the pound. We carry a variety of drinks from hot foamy lattes or rich cappuccinos to iced specialty coffee drinks. Lounge in our cafe and browse the web while enjoying your dessert and coffee.

Seasonal and Local
We refuse to compromise on quality in our restaurant. That's why we source our fresh ingredients from local farmers' markets. We bake our breads and desserts on site. We wash and slice our produce here, to guarantee freshness and quality.
